snippet.title: MANDI BIRYANI | 3 Full Goat Arabian Mutton Mandi Recipe Cooking In Village | Kuzhi Mandhi Biryani
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook mutton mandi recipe by cooking three full goats. Kuzhi Mandi recipe is one of the famous Arabian food which is cooking meat and rice together in underground. We do the same traditional Arabian method to get the real taste of the mandi Recipe.

 We tasted Mutton Mandhi for the first time in our life! Really Tasty!

snippet.title: Noori (Official Music Video) | Fukra Insaan X Komal | Drishti Kharbanda | Indiea Records
snippet.description:
This one is super special!
Noori is all about those unforgettable memories and that one-of-a-kind love that can't be duplicated by anyone else.
Y‚Äôall killed it with the teaser, so show as much and more support for the song!
Let me know your favourite part in the comments below.
 
Singer: Fukra Insaan & Komal Sohi
Music, Lyrics & Composition - Jaskaran Singh
Mixed & Mastered by: Mukul Jain
Director /DOP - Manish Shunty 
Production designer - Shubra Shah
Chief AD - Adit thakur 
DOP assistant - Abhishek 
Editor/Colorist-Mr.luvv
Line producers: Monty Production
Art : Rahul 
Still making : J Singh 
Makup artist : Aamir 
Spot team : Shubam 
Steady cam : Sandeep 
Jimmy jib : Vicky 
Production team : Harry and Gagan 
Transport : Hindustan 
Drone operator: harwinder 
Light : Devraj and deva films 
Camra : Cinedream 
Local boy hp : Rahul Sloni 
Food : Monoj Catering 

In association with CollabX Entertainment

Lyrics :
Tenu karan yaad inhaa jinaa koi kar nahi sakda
Tenu karan pyaar inhaa jinaa koi kar nahi sakda
 
tu meriyan ve saari gallan janda
mai tetho sanga sab tu pehchhanda
Way sarda na hove jado dur tu
haal ankhan vicho padh mutiyaar da
 
tera jeya sachi ve koi sohna ni
ae kehn da tareeka koi hona ni
paleya mai tenu kade khone ni
Mai vi karan tenu pyar
 
Mai kol tere v awa
Te naal tenu bithawa
Je pyar kara madi tenu
Te pyar hi mai v chawa
Karan kadar tere mai pyar di
Tan hi khushi tenu din raat dava
Mai na hor kise de naal dissa
Bas tenu hi mai chawa
 
Tenu rakha way mai dil ch wassa k
Noor way bna k zindagi tu meriye
Teri ankh wich surmaa mai paa k
Kol way bitha k karan gallan teriyeee
 
Tenu karan yaad inhaa jinaa koi kar nahi sakda
Tenu karan pyaar inhaa jinaa koi kar nahi sakda

Abhishek also addresses each and every controversy of his and also the one related to Elvish and shares his Bollywood aspirations.

snippet.title: Garden Vegetables Steffi Ulagam | Harvesting Vegetgables from Home Garden in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video join me as I harvest some vegetables from home garden. As the hot summer has passed away, now the pleasant weather has begun. We grow a lot of vegetables and fruits and always harvesting home grown vegetables is a pleasant experience. Alandra also like working in the garden. We have also setup some bird feeder for feeding some birds during the summer months and providing them with water. 

Friends, please do give gardening a try and it is a very relaxing hobby and will keep you firmly rooted. Thanks for watching and I will update you on future vlogs.

4x4 aale jhaaj chale kheta mai
Dhai dhai fute  re  ye faal ghadge  
Puri marda dhad sawraj chale reta mai
Kisana aala jhanda dekh juhle se bolero pe
Bharle mulak  chora ghume se camero pe
Hoke ka shokeen mhara daily ka routine

Jma pke kite chalre chdhai pe
Speed puri high pe

Na koi bahas na debate sare chatri chraite
Makha aa lie re nagana ke naag laanie
Saale beria ke sanjh pehla daag laanie
Mukhaymantri ki gel chale fire birgade
Or mhari gelya chale niri aag laanie
Dashborda mai asle ptash lie ghume
Maut ka sman sara khas lie ghume
Prshashan bhi aapas mai horya confuse 
Re ye kon the jo diggia mai lash lie ghume
 
Chandigarh k mah chale choudhar k role
Or chaudhary se chore haryane aale re 
Parne ka marke mandasa chale se 
Chite kurte pajamw desi baane aale re 
Mharra hov geda log rally maane se
Chale motra p  fun log belly maane se
Bina kam gaadia rel si bnaye rakhe
Bera ni kyu log saale kali maane se 
Sutli k bumb jisi teri h sthithi hum

snippet.title: Hamas Asks Gaza to Defy Evac Order, Israel Seeks "Clear" China Condemnation, Nasrallah-Iran¬†FM¬†Meet
snippet.description:
Israel‚Äôs military has admitted it would take time for Palestinians to follow its orders to evacuate north Gaza. IDF says Israel's military is aware that evacuating 1.1 million people from northern Gaza - as Israel has called for - will take some time.
‚ÄúI will not say [if] it‚Äôs an accurate time,‚Äù Hagari added when asked to confirm the army had informed UN officials Palestinians had 24 hours to flee
Meanwhile, Hamas has called on Palestinian residents to defy an Israeli order to evacuate the northern part of the Gaza Strip.
‚ÄúWe tell the people of northern Gaza and from Gaza City, stay put in your homes, and your places‚Äù, Hamas Spokesperson Eyad Al-Bozom said. 
Israel expressed ‚Äúdeep disappointment‚Äù in a call with the Chinese envoy to the Middle East over China‚Äôs lack of condemnation of Hamas‚Äôs attack. According to the ministry, the Chinese statements "do not provide a clear and unambiguous condemnation of the horrific terrorist acts.‚Äù

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3901 | 13 Oct 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3901: Goli Ka Confusion
--------------------------------------------------------
Goli modifies into Lord Ganesha, and Bhakti's request is finally realized. The little girl is overjoyed, which makes her parents happy. Goli chooses to keep Garba and Bhakti together before leaving. He begins the dance with Bhakti, but eventually, all of the Gokuldham members join in. Goli dances with purposeful zeal, making it difficult for everyone to keep up with him. Bhide and Sodhi were panting with weariness, but Goli kept going. Following the Garba Act, all Gokuldham inhabitants were exhausted, and Bhakti and her parents expressed gratitude for their support before departure.

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3901, 13 Oct 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3900 | 12 Oct 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3900: Bhakti Ka Sapa Hua Poora
--------------------------------------------------------
When Bhakti sees Lord Ganesh giving 'darshan' for the first time to her, she becomes extremely joyful and emotional. She hugs and plays garba with him and asks him to call the members of Gokudlham as well who had helped her in her penance. The Gokuldham members are contacted later by Bhakti to meet her god as they were hidden in the clubhouse as per the plan. Is this Goli or someone else dressed as God? See the episode to find out what happens next!

Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni

Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Inside the Gaza siege - an eyewitness report
snippet.description:
The Gaza Strip has been sealed off by the Israeli military, and its residents - around 2.3 million Palestinians - are feeling the full force of their neighbour's wrath. 

(Subscribe: https://bit.ly/C4_News_Subscribe) 

We can't get inside Gaza to report on what is going on, but our colleague - filmmaker Yousef Hammash - lives there. 

This is his eyewitness report and a warning: it is distressing from the start.

snippet.title: The Apartment | EP 03 | Ft. Bigg Boss Abhirami, Ajay Melvin | Love Web Series | Love Series | JFW |
snippet.description:
The Apartment - A Story of a Mismatched Couple is a 6 episode tamil web series by JFW featuring Abhirami Venkatachalam and Ajay Melvin!  Get ready to fall in love with the quirkiest Rom Com Duo as we introduce Sam and Vidya whose unique chemistry promises to make this story one for the ages!

Episode 3 - Fading Colours
Sam and Vidya have an intimate night together for the first time after they have got into a relationship. Sam is worried if the love between him and Vidya are real and if he can get used to sharing his personal space with Vidya! Watch the episode and find out more!

#jfw #jfworiginals #jfwwebseries #theapartment #romcom #romanticcomedy #abhiramivenkatachalam #abhirami #ajay #ajaymelvin #leo #leotrailer #vijay #trisha #nipponpaint #presta

snippet.title: Children 'mercilessly' killed by Hamas in Israel massacre - as Gaza is pummelled
snippet.description:
The unprecedented response promised by Israel in the wake of the weekend's atrocities has now well and truly clicked into gear.

Earlier, the Israeli military said it had secured the border with Gaza, which is now under the heaviest bombardment in its history

Meanwhile, residents in the Israeli city of Ashkelon - close to that border - were warned to take shelter by Hamas militants. 

A salvo of rocket fire then followed, the extent of the damage is still unclear.

Our Foreign Affairs Correspondent Secunder Kermani has been to the Kfar Aza kibbutz - one of those targeted by the militants on Saturday.

localized.title: Children 'mercilessly' killed by Hamas in Israel massacre - as Gaza is pummelled
localized.description:
The unprecedented response promised by Israel in the wake of the weekend's atrocities has now well and truly clicked into gear.

Earlier, the Israeli military said it had secured the border with Gaza, which is now under the heaviest bombardment in its history

Meanwhile, residents in the Israeli city of Ashkelon - close to that border - were warned to take shelter by Hamas militants. 

A salvo of rocket fire then followed, the extent of the damage is still unclear.

Our Foreign Affairs Correspondent Secunder Kermani has been to the Kfar Aza kibbutz - one of those targeted by the militants on Saturday.
